      "span_text": "), growth arrest and DNA-damage-inducible beta (GADD45B), protein-tyrosine phosphatase receptor type O gene (PTPRO) and thrombospondin, type I, domain containing 1 (THSD1) genes was determined by methylation-specific polymerase chain reaction (MSP) with 1 µl of bisulfite-treated DNA as template and AmpliTaq Gold 360 Master Mix (Applied Biosystems, Foster City, CA, USA) for amplification, as previously described [CITATION_1] .",
